# Markdown is owned by markdownlint (.markdownlint-cli2.jsonc), NOT prettier.
#
# Two formatters on one file type fight: prettier pads table columns and reflows content, which is
# exactly the style this repo does not use (see MD060 in the markdownlint config) — and it would rewrite
# specs/BACKLOG.md's 1600-char table rows. Keeping prettier off .md is what stops `pnpm run format` from
# silently undoing `pnpm run lint:md:fix`.
#
# One owner per file type: prettier → code, markdownlint → markdown.
*.md

